    <h4>Ingredients:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>1 ripe banana</li>
        <li>1/4 cup oats (instant or rolled)</li>
        <li>1 cup milk (or almond milk)</li>
        <li>1 tsp honey or maple syrup</li>
        <li>1/4 tsp cinnamon (optional)</li>
        <li>3-4 ice cubes</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Instructions:</h4>
    <ol>
        <li>Add banana, oats, milk, honey, cinnamon, and ice cubes to a blender.</li>
        <li>Blend until smooth and creamy.</li>
        <li>Pour into a glass and serve chilled.</li>
    </ol>
